Seven irregragable propositions concerning oaths Dedicated to King Charles I. By the right reverend Dr. Jos. Hall, then Lord Bishop of Exon. And printed in the year 1639. Hall, Joseph, 1574-1656.
3, [1] p.
s.n., [London? : 1700?]
Caption title; suggested imprint from Wing. Concerns oaths and covenants; a reprinting of the 1639 edition (STC 12646b). Lacks the dedication to King Charles I and the two 'corollaries' and has in addition a section with caption title: Questions concerning the validity of the late Act for the oath of abjuration. Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
